<hymn_number>6964</hymn_number>
<title>ywmaⁿạ bʿd ywm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ywmạaⁿ bʿd ywm mndẖ ḥrrtny tạ̉ty ạ̹ly wtrfʿny
 ʿndmạ ạ̉dẖkr mạḍy tryny mstqbly ywmạaⁿ bʿd ywm
 ywmạaⁿ bʿd ywm tḍmny ạ̹lyk sydy ạ̉nt sẖfạʾy
 sydy ạ̉nt wḥdk ḥbyby yswʿ ạ̉ḥbk
 yswʿ ạ̉ḥbk yswʿ ạ̹ny lk yạ yswʿ
 wạnt ly yạ ḥbyby yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>